snippet.title: Longplay of Arcade Hits: Moon Patrol & Spy Hunter
snippet.description:
Longplay of Arcade Hits: Moon Patrol & Spy Hunter, played as the PAL version on the Game Boy Color. This game's version was released on May 1st, 1999. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

00:00 - Start
00:30 - Moon Patrol
12:36 - Spy Hunter
35:11 - Credits

By: Terua
